            loading="lazy"
          />

          <img
            src="/images/logos/mcdonalds.svg"
            alt="mcdonalds logo"
            loading="lazy"
          />

          <img src="/images/logos/huma.svg" alt="huma logo" loading="lazy" />

          <img
            src="/images/logos/capital-one.svg"
            alt="capital-one logo"
            loading="lazy"
          />

          <img
            src="/images/logos/home/airbyte.svg"
            alt="airbyte logo"
            loading="lazy"
          />

          <img
            src="/images/logos/betterment.svg"
            alt="betterment logo"
            loading="lazy"
          />

          <img
            src="/images/logos/deutsche-telekom.svg"
            alt="Deutsche Telekom logo"
            loading="lazy"
          />

          <img src="/images/logos/kong.svg" alt="kong logo" loading="lazy" />
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-container flex-row-reverse container">
        <div>
          <h2>What's the difference between Metabase and Tableau</h2>
          <p>
            <a href="/case-studies/alto"
              >Tableau has a steeper learning curve than Metabase</a
            >. People (even non-technical or data-savvy folks) actually like
            using Metabase, because it‚Äôs easier to learn, meaning they‚Äôre more
            likely to run reports and get data on their own.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <video
            class="vjs-player lazy w-100 pause-observer autoplay-video"
            autoplay=""
            muted=""
            playsinline=""
            poster="/images/landing-pages/hero-query-builder.gif"
          >
            <source
              src="/images/landing-pages/hero-query-builder.mp4"
              type="video/mp4"
            />

            <p class="vjs-no-js">
              To view this video please enable JavaScript and consider upgrading
              to a web browser that
              <a href="https://videojs.com/html5-video-support/" target="_blank"
                >supports HTML5 video</a
              >
            </p>
          </video>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-container container two-checklists">
        <div>
          <h2>What makes Metabase a good choice compared to Tableau?</h2>
          <p></p>

          <ul class="checklist-outline">
            <li>
              <b>Easy to use for everyone.</b> With intuitive tools like <a
                href="/features/analytics-dashboards">interactive dashboards</a
              > with quick drill-through analyses, <a
                href="/features/query-builder"
                >the query builder to write questions without SQL</a
              >, and one-click-to-create charts.
            </li>

            <li>
              <b>Open source and affordable.</b>
              <a href="/pricing/">Transparent pricing</a> for startups through to
              advanced functionality and support for Enterprise.
            </li>

            <li>
              <b
                >Super fast to set up and integrate with what‚Äôs in your stack.</b
              > Go from <a href="https://store.metabase.com/checkout"
                >install to creating your first dashboard in less than 5 minutes</a
              >. No technical skills or data team required.
            </li>

            <li>
              <b>Help from our world class Success team.</b> Technical experts who
              help with everything from troubleshooting to advice on best practices.
              Customers <i>love</i> them.
            </li>

            <li>
              <b>Private and secure.</b>
